SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 5773
A bill to amend 1978 PA 368, entitled
"Public health code,"
(MCL 333.1101 to 333.25211) by adding section 16282a.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
1 Sec. 16282a. A licensee or registrant shall refer a patient to
2 a diagnostic center for fetal alcohol spectrum disorder that has
3 been identified by the department of health and human services as a
4 center of excellence if the patient is a minor who the licensee or
5 registrant treats for a condition related to prenatal alcohol
6 exposure.
